title: Google\Cloud\AIPlatform\V1\Featurestore\OnlineServingConfig
name: OnlineServingConfig
description:
OnlineServingConfig specifies the details for provisioning online serving resources.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.aiplatform.v1.Featurestore.OnlineServingConfig

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.fixed_node_count
params.description: The number of nodes for the online store. The number of nodes doesn't scale automatically, but you can manually update the number of nodes. If set to 0, the featurestore will not have an online store and cannot be used for online serving.

params.name: data.scaling
params.description: Online serving scaling configuration. Only one of fixed_node_count and scaling can be set. Setting one will reset the other.
